1. *Oni su večeras dugo razgovarali*. (They talked a lot tonight.)
2. *Oni su se razgovarali o njegovom putovanju*. (They talked about his trip.)
3. *Ona je razgovarala sa njim satima*. (She talked with him for hours.)
4. *On se razgovarao sa svojim prijateljima*. (He was talking with his friends.)
5. *Ona će razgovarati sa njim sutra*. (She will talk with him tomorrow.)
6. *Mi ćemo razgovarati o tome kasnije*. (We will talk about it later.)